    <section>
      <div>
        <h5>Projects:</h5>
        <div class="project">
          <div class="text wrap flex space-bw" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#learnest" data-controller="accordion-icon" data-action="click->accordion-icon#iconToggle">
            <div><p>Learnest Web App</p></div>
            <div><p>2022<i class="fas fa-solid fa-plus" data-accordion-icon-target="icon"></i></p></div>
          </div>
          <div id="learnest" class="collapse">
            <div class="content">
              <%= image_tag("Learnest.jpg")%>
              <p>Three teammates and I built a question and answer web app for post-secondary students and teachers, <%= link_to "Learnest", "https://learnest-app.herokuapp.com/", target: :_blank, class: "project-links"%>, as a final project in Le Wagon's web development bootcamp.</p>
              <p>My main backend contributions included web scraping and then storing, parsing and importing the JSON seed file.</p>
              <p>My main frontend contributions included overall brand and UX/UI design, the homepage, question and answer card design and responsiveness.</p>
              <p>Tech: Ruby on Rails, Heroku, PostgreSQL, Javascript, StimulusJS, HTML, SCSS, Bootstrap, Devise Authentication, Pundit Authorization, Nokogiri Parsing</p>
              <p class="project-links"><%= link_to "Learnest", "https://learnest-app.herokuapp.com/", target: :_blank %></p>
              <p class="project-links"><%= link_to "Demo Presentation", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EtgwZE8tK1M&t=1031s", target: :_blank %></p>
              <p class="project-links"><%= link_to "GitHub", "https://github.com/ConnorSand/Learnest", target: :_blank %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
          <div class="text wrap flex space-bw" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#standupFinder" data-controller="accordion-icon" data-action="click->accordion-icon#iconToggle">
            <div>Standup Finder Web App</div>
            <div><p>2022<i class="fas fa-solid fa-plus" data-accordion-icon-target="icon"></i></p></div>
          </div>
          <div id="standupFinder" class="collapse">
            <div class="content">
              <%= image_tag("StandupFinder.jpg")%>
              <p>Three teammates and I built a two-sided marketplace web app for booking and listing stand-up comedy shows, <%= link_to "Standup Finder", "https://comedy-app.herokuapp.com/", target: :_blank, class: "project-links"%>, as a project in Le Wagon's web development bootcamp. The idea came from a stand-up comedian friend of mine, <%= link_to "Jordan Gray", "https://www.jordanthomasgray.com/", target: :_blank, class: "project-links"%></p>
              <p>My main backend contributions included setting up routes, models and controllers, the skeleton index view and the geocoded map feature.</p>
              <p>My main frontend contributions included overall brand and UX/UI design, the homepage and index card design.</p>
              <p>Tech: Ruby on Rails, Heroku, PostgreSQL, Javascript, StimulusJS, HTML, SCSS, Bootstrap, Devise Authentication, Geocoder, Mapbox API</p>
              <p class="project-links"><%= link_to "Standup Finder", "https://comedy-app.herokuapp.com/", target: :_blank %></p>
              <p class="project-links"><%= link_to "GitHub", "https://github.com/Brianhuynh97/Comedy-app", target: :_blank %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
          <div class="text wrap flex space-bw" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#digitalConsulting" data-controller="accordion-icon" data-action="click->accordion-icon#iconToggle">
            <div>Freelance Digital Consulting</div>
            <div><p>2021 - 2022<i class="fas fa-solid fa-plus" data-accordion-icon-target="icon"></i></p></div>
          </div>
          <div id="digitalConsulting" class="collapse">
            <div class="content">
              <%= image_tag("DigitalConsulting.jpg")%>
              <p>I worked as a freelance digital consultant while transitioning to a new career as a full stack web developer.</p>
              <p>I provided services in the following areas:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Brand and Content Consulting - Advising on brand, content and tone-of-voice guidelines for B2B and B2C marketing materials</li>
                <li>SEO Product Management - Directing SEO content strategy and implementation for e-commerce marketplaces, working with developers and managing freelance copywriters</li>
                <li>Digital Transformation Consulting - Leading business operations process improvement, digitisation and automation</li>
              </ul>
              <p>See <%= link_to "LinkedIn", "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sarah-m-pelham/", target: :_blank, class: "project-links"%> for more career details.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
